{# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  SYSTEM INSTRUCTIONS – shown once per request                             #
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #}
{% set sys_prompt %}
You are a professional multiple-choice question (MCQ) solver.

• Carefully read the question and the numbered options.
• Provide your reasoning for the correct option in English, using up to 7 sentences.
• After your explanation, write exactly one line in the following format:

Correct option: ****n****

where n is the number (from 1 to N) of the correct choice.

**Do not write any extra text before or after this line. Any change in the format of this final line will be considered an error.**
{% endset -%}

{# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  FEW-SHOT EXAMPLES                                                         #
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #}
{% for ex in shots %}
<|begin_of_example|>
Question: {{ ex.question }}
{% for i, choice in enumerate(ex.choices, 1) -%}
{{ i }}) {{ choice }}
{% endfor %}
Answer: {{ ex.rationale }}
Correct option: ****{{ ex.answer }}****
<|end_of_example|>

{% endfor -%}

{# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  QUERY INSTANCE                                                            #
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #}
<|system|>
{{ sys_prompt }}
<|end|>

Question: {{ question }}
{% for i, choice in enumerate(choices, 1) -%}
{{ i }}) {{ choice }}
{% endfor %}

Write your answer in English according to the instructions above, and write the final line exactly as specified.
